title: Temple of the Spider Priest
story: The Spider Priest is long gone, but people are still reluctant to come close to the temple. Currently it is overrun with scorpions, which don't care about the past of the place. The temple of the Spider Priest is home to a rare specie of berries.

notes.text: A large iron door on the eastern wall.
A bony gnome, lying on the ground.
A still warm body of a kobold, a lamp close to it.
A creepy doll, tells an unwanted truth when picked up.
A reinforced crate holds a bronze chess piece.
A tapestry on the wall depicting the land around the temple.
A mosaic of a leaf pattern on the walls
